<figureCitation id="B9949B66335DE58166AEF5A1D4E4AEB0" captionStart="Figure 3" captionStartId="F3" captionText="Figure 3. Jezonogonalos eburnalva Zhang &amp; Chen, sp. nov., holotype, male (En- 419020) A tyloids on 10 th- 16 th segments of antenna B wings C head, lateral aspect D mesosoma, dorsal aspect E mesosoma, lateral aspect F metasoma, dorsal aspect G metasoma, lateral aspect H metasoma, ventral aspect." figureDoi="10.3897/jhr.90.80150.figure3" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/677740" pageId="0" pageNumber="101">, 3</figureCitation>
